    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tTablet\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Chard deNiord\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cHad he not grieved so deeply, \nhe never would have grown into the comedian he did\u201d\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPoetry\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/poetry/7888/tablet-chard-deniord"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Art of Fiction No. 254\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Sigrid Nunez\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cThis is a hard thing to say, but it\u2019s absolutely true\u2014when I think of the men I\u2019ve been with, every one of them stood between me and my writing.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInterviews\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/interviews/7906/the-art-of-fiction-no-254-sigrid-nunez"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tWhy Write?\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Elisa Gabbert\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 6, 2022\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cI\u2019ve been collecting these theories of why writers write because so many writers have written about it.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Daily\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tArts & Culture\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
