    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRiccardo\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Dan Bevacqua\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cMy parents loved each other, but their love confused them. Witnessing their marriage was like watching a dog bark at the door when no one\u2019s there.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFiction\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
