      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tIra & the Whale\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Rachel B. Glaser\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cIra wonders for an insane moment if he is seeing art \u2026 but then remembers he is trapped in a whale and will die alone.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFiction\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
